modShortDescription: Adds a workstation where you can craft most mod schematics, and some item and weapon schematics.
modDescription:
Adds a workstation where you can craft most mod schematics, and some item and weapon schematics.

Workstation is gated behind Advanced Engineering Rank 3, but the schematic can be found in the wild!

**Important:** Needs to be installed on both the server and client sides, due to custom icon(s)/assets.

**[Download](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1sKWCo4lhZ3GjEqHgiBTvNTu5eIfhwbes/view?usp=sharing)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/20806-freakuks-modlets/).
